name: upbeat_goldwasser
command:
sh -c 'mkdir -p /codefresh/volume/pvpvj && cat /dev/null > /codefresh/volume/pvpvj/cf_export && chmod 774 /codefresh/volume/pvpvj/cf_export && cat > /codefresh/volume/pvpvj/cf_export <<zzz23EndOfMessagezzz23 #!/usr/bin/env sh
set -e
IFS=''
arg=
for arg in \$@; do
    case "\$arg" in
    
        *=*)
        printf "Exporting \$arg
" 
        echo "\$arg" >> /codefresh/volume/pvpvj/env_vars_to_export
        echo "\$arg" >> /codefresh/volume/env_vars_to_export
        ;;
        
        *)
        eval 'varValue=$'"\$arg"
        printf "Exporting \$arg=\$varValue
" 
        echo "\$arg=\$varValue" >> /codefresh/volume/pvpvj/env_vars_to_export
        echo "\$arg=\$varValue" >> /codefresh/volume/env_vars_to_export
        
    esac

done
zzz23EndOfMessagezzz23
'
